---
<footer class="border-t border-[color:var(--color-line-soft)]"
  style="padding: clamp(32px, 5vw, 48px) clamp(20px, 4vw, 80px) clamp(24px, 3vw, 32px);">

  <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:justify-between items-center gap-6 lg:gap-10 mb-6">
    <div class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.2em] opacity-60 text-center lg:text-left"
         style="font-family: var(--font-mono);">
      TRAIL DES TECTOSAGES · VIEILLE-TOULOUSE · MMXXVI
    </div>
    <div class="flex gap-5 sm:gap-10 items-center">
      <div class="logo-tile" style="padding: 10px;">
        <img src="/images/logo-lions.png" alt="Lions Club Toulouse Arènes Romaines"
             style="height: clamp(50px, 6vw, 70px); object-fit: contain;" />
      </div>
      <div class="logo-tile" style="padding: 10px;">
        <img src="/images/logo-marie-louise.png" alt="Fondation Marie-Louise"
             style="height: clamp(44px, 6vw, 70px); object-fit: contain;" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="text-center leading-[1.8] opacity-40 text-[9px] sm:text-[10px] tracking-[0.18em]"
       style="font-family: var(--font-mono);">
    ASSOCIATION TRAIL DES TECTOSAGES · COMITÉ DES FÊTES · LIONS CLUB TOULOUSE ARÈNES ROMAINES · FONDATION MARIE-LOUISE
  </div>
</footer>
